MBOMBELA &#8211; Environmental activists achieved victory over the Department of Mineral Resources (DMR) this week in their battle to safeguard the Elands and Crocodile rivers and Dullstroom&#8217;s trout farms.The Pretoria High Court granted an order to compel the minister of mineral resources to make a decision on the two appeals lodged by BirdLife SA and the Escarpment Environment Protection Group (EEPOG).